noise, which means you go, mmm.

00:02:41.540 --> 00:02:43.490
Like on the top of
mouth and tongue.

00:02:43.490 --> 00:02:44.270
Just like, mmm.

00:02:44.270 --> 00:02:45.097
Everybody go, mmm.

