00:57:42.690 --> 00:57:43.900
And is it being recorded?

00:57:43.900 --> 00:57:44.930
Is this being captured?

00:57:44.930 --> 00:57:47.074
Like, we need to have
these conversations here.

00:57:47.074 --> 00:57:48.240
So thank you for coming out.

00:57:48.240 --> 00:57:49.790
We have a little gift for you.

